Description: StrayLight OS desktop applications for Linux window managers
 Built-in desktop applications (terminal, file manager, system monitor,
 settings, wizard, OOBE, app GUI control panels), native app CLI launch/help
 entrypoints, themes, firstboot helpers, and Calamares installer configuration.
 These tools run on the
 distribution-provided desktop and window manager; no StrayLight compositor
 is shipped or required by this package.
